<!-- About Us Section -->
<section class="about-section">
  <div class="container text-left">
    <h2>About Furever Home</h2>
    <p>
      FureverHome is dedicated to helping pets find their forever homes. Our platform connects loving adopters with pets in need,
      creating a seamless experience for both pet owners and adopters. We believe that every pet deserves a safe, loving home,
      and we're here to make that happen.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Mission Section -->
<section class="mission-section">
  <div class="container text-left">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>
      Our mission is to reduce the number of homeless pets by providing a trusted and accessible platform for pet adoption.
      We strive to empower adopters, owners, and shelters by offering an easy-to-use service that facilitates meaningful
      connections between people and pets. By working together, we can give every pet the love and care they deserve.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

